  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a double-blind, placebo-controled, randomized trial to investigate if aspirin
      pre-treatment has anti-inflammatory effects in a model of acute lung injury induced by
      inhaled endotoxin (LPS) in healthy human volunteers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
